                <a href="https://www.politico.com/magazine/story/2018/02/18/whats-missing-from-the-gun-debate-217022" target="_top" data-tracking="mpos=page-top&mid=teasebox&lindex=1&lcol=5" class="js-tealium-tracking"><img data-lazy-img="https://static.politico.com/dims4/default/11ab83f/2147483647/legacy_thumbnail/167x91%3E/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.politico.com%2Ff7%2Ff3%2F20a5301c482aa3203523ebc5a728%2F180218gunsgettyimages-918716578.jpg" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="Semi-automatic AR-15s are pictured. | Getty Images" data-size="promo_small"></a></div>
